1374,21120162", "polymorphism": "Non-Polymorphism", "variant_interpret_cn": "该变异在ExAC数据库NFE人群频率为0.0008264（55/66556），gnomADe数据库ASJ人群频率为0.0005967（6/10056）、gnomADg数据库FIN人群频率为0.0005757（2/3474），1000G数据库无记录；在骨髓增生性疾病患者（PMID: 15858187, PMID: 2112016）、真性红细胞增多症患者（PMID: 15793561, PMID: 20631743）、骨髓增值性肿瘤患者（PMID: 22818858）、骨髓肉瘤和骨髓纤维化继发性急性髓系白血病患者（PMID: 22041374）中曾有报道；文献报道，该变异在患者中频率显著高于对照（PMID: 20631743, PMID: 21120162, PMID: 22818858, PMID： 15858187, PMID: 20631743）。该变异在ClinVar数据库报道为Conflicting_interpretations_of_pathogenicity（Pathogenic,Uncertain_significance）（ID=14662，可靠度为一颗星）。蛋白功能研究显示，该变异影响蛋白功能（PMID: 15793561, PMID: 15858187）。基于整合预测工具REVEL认为该变异为disease-causing。", "variant_interpret_en": "", "variant_desc_cn": "该变异为错义突变，导致基因编码蛋白第617位氨基酸由缬氨酸突变为苯丙氨酸。", "variant_desc_en": "", "evidence_categorys": "PP3;PS3;PS4", "evi_sum": [], "drug_var": {"drug_names": [], "var": {"gene_symbol": "JAK2", "gene_region": "exon14", "hgvs_p_abbr": "p.Val617Phe", "hgvs_c": "c.1849G>T", "hgvs_p": "p.V617F"}}, "gene_function": "JAK2基因属于原癌基因，编码酪氨酸蛋白激酶JAK2，是一种非受体蛋白酪氨酸激酶，可结合细胞因子受体激活干扰素-α/β/γ途径，是JAK/STAT信号通路的成员（PMID: 15575979; PMID: 30092288）。目前，已经在多种肿瘤类型中观察到JAK2基因突变，如骨髓增生性肿瘤（PMID: 30074114）、淋巴瘤（PMID: 29984752）、白血病（PMID: 29979407）和宫颈癌（PMID: 30003068）。"}, {"sample_id": "S22090311PD01", "order_code": "5a2101e033da11eda9f00242c0a89006", "bio_category": "Snvindel", "gene_symbol": "STK11", "transcript_primary": "NM_000455.5", "var_id": "65fc7fd68b486cd31c666fc356a36cbf", "hgvs_c": "c.723T>C", "hgvs_p": "p.(A241=)", "hgvs_p_abbr": "p.(Ala241=)", "chr": "chr19", "start": "1220705", "end": "1220705", "ref": "T", "alt": "C", "gene_region": "exon5", "freq": 0.4914, "freq_case": 0.4914, "freq_ctrl": 0.5011, "freq_ss": 0.4864, "freq_sc": null, "type": "Synonymous_Substitution", "tag": "PASS;Germline;PW;WBC;IC", "igvplot": "/var/www/html/report_backend/system_files/json_file/20220919_SHXW_A000259_ADXPAN116-Pair_v0.3.0.export20229209959/S22090311PD01_S22090311PD01L01_AH7MLMDRX2_1/IGV/chr19_1220705_1220705.svg", "depth": 6150.0, "json_batch_name": "20220919_SHXW_A000259_ADXPAN116-Pair_v0.3.0.export20229209959", "var_origin": "germline", "clinical_significance": "Likely benign", "function_classification": "Likely benign", "clinical_category": "Tier IV", "literature": "", "polymorphism": "Non-Polymorphism", "variant_interpret_cn": "该变异在1000G数据库EAS_CHB人群频率为0.009709（2/206），ExAC、gnomADe、gnomADg数据库EAS人群频率分别为0.002280（19/8334）、0.002356（42/17826）、0.001284（2/1558）；在ClinVar数据库报道为Benign/Likely_benign（ID=135927，可靠度为两颗星）。基于剪接预测软件SpliceAI认为该变异不影响剪接。", "variant_interpret_en": "", "variant_desc_cn": "该变异为同义突变。", "variant_desc_en": "", "evidence_categorys": "BP6;BP7;BS1", "evi_sum": [], "drug_var": {"drug_names": [], "var": {"gene_symbol": "STK11", "gene_region": "exon5", "hgvs_p_abbr": "p.(Ala241=)", "hgvs_c": "c.723T>C", "hgvs_p": "p.(A241=)"}}, "gene_function": "STK11基因属于抑癌基因，编码丝氨酸/苏氨酸激酶11，通过与STRAD和MO25形成具有生物活性的异质三聚体，从而激活AMPK通路(PMID: 18439900)，STK11-AMPK信号调节细胞代谢和能量稳态，以及细胞对DNA损伤和营养缺乏的应激反应(PMID: 21396365)。STK11的激活可抑制下游mTOR的活性（PMID: 21396365; PMID: 20160076），STK11的缺失已被证明会导致细胞极性紊乱和肿瘤在营养不良的条件下生长。STK11基因突变在多种肿瘤中均有报道，在肺癌、乳腺癌、宫颈癌、睾丸癌、肝癌以及恶性黑色素瘤、胰腺癌和胆道癌等肿瘤(PMID: 25244018)。"}], "sv": [], "cnv": [], "cnv_file_path": [], "rna_sv": [], "mlpa": [], "hrd": [], "msi": [], "tmb": [], "pdl1": [], "knb": [], "ec_type": [], "cdx": [{"gene_symbol": "ALK", "tumor_group_id": "1", "tumor_name_cn": "非小细胞肺癌", "tumor_name_en": "Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer"}, {"gene_symbol": "BRAF", "tumor_group_id": "1", "tumor_name_cn": "非小细胞肺癌", "tumor_name_en": "Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer"}, {"gene_symbol": "EGFR", "tumor_group_id": "1", "tumor_name_cn": "非小细胞肺癌", "tumor_name_en": "Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer"}, {"gene_symbol": "ERBB2", "tumor_group_id": "1", "tumor_name_cn": "非小细胞肺癌", "tumor_name_en": "Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer"}, {"gene_symbol": "KRAS", "tumor_group_id": "1", "tumor_name_cn": "非小细胞肺癌", "tumor_name_en": "Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer"}, {"gene_symbol": "MET", "tumor_group_id": "1", "tumor_name_cn": "非小细胞肺癌", "tumor_name_en":